# Verification required

After implementing or modifying code in this repo:

1. Run `make verify` from the project root.
2. Fix any failures before telling the user the task is done.
3. For UI changes, ensure `e2e/smoke.spec.ts` still passes (uses `data-testid` selectors).

See `AGENTS.md` for details on the test stack and partial commands.
